When was the last time you let yourself fully receive?
Not advice, not another to-do list—but deep, nourishing rest?

What would it feel like to be held in sound, to let your body soften and your nervous system exhale?
If your soul has been craving a pause… this is your invitation.

Join us Sunday, July 13th at 7:45 PM at Astoria Yoga for a deep sound bath + guided meditation designed to support emotional release, nervous system healing, and energetic reset.

We’ll drop into a space where crystal bowls, chimes, and grounding frequency meet your breath and intention. This isn’t just a class—it’s a recalibration.

🧘🏽‍♀️ Come alone or bring someone who needs a soft landing too.
✨ No experience necessary—just bring your open heart and something cozy to lie on.

💫 Space is limited, so claim your spot now:
🔗 LINK IN MY BIO!!! 

Your rest is sacred.
Your healing is now.

Join us for an unforgettable evening of connection, creativity, and celebration 🥳🌈

RSVP via link in bio!

From 7:00 to 9:00 PM, this immersive brand showcase brings together a handpicked collective of visionaries and purpose-driven brands — all rooted in plant-based living, human connection, and creative excellence.

Your Hosts:

Davina Rae’s
A bold and beautifully crafted hot sauce brand, bringing vibrant flavor and cultural storytelling to every bottle. Designed to elevate plant-based cooking — and spark conversation.

DOM Interiors
An award-winning Italian kitchen and design showroom in the heart of SoHo, offering cutting-edge craftsmanship and modern elegance — the perfect backdrop for this evening of creativity and community.

Sunday Supper
A craveable, plant-powered frozen food brand offering vegan, gluten-free, and non-GMO single-serve entrées and appetizers — indulgent, healthy, and crafted for togetherness.

VEGPRENEUR
The world’s largest plant-based business community. Learn more and join: vegpreneur.org (http://vegpreneur.org/)

Expect an evening of elevated botanical beverages, vibrant plant-based bites, and inspired brand installations that embody wellness, integrity, innovation, and joy.

This is a private, invite-only gathering for a community rooted in collaboration, creativity, and shared purpose — a constellation of aligned humans building together.

Dress how you feel. Be who you are. Be fancy. Be proud.

Showcasing Brands:
18 Chestnuts, Abbot’s, Afterdream THC Social Tonic, Ciao Pappi, Clover Caramels, Davina Rae’s, Folk Revival, Good Twin Sparkling Non-Alc Wine, RIND, Sunday Supper, Summer Water Rosé, Treeline Cheese, Urban Vegan Kitchen, Whoa! Dough.
